.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, d&b, hip-hop, house, pop, soul, trance
City: edinburgh, miami, marseilles, hannover, berlin, prague, new-york
 1. the person traveling to hannover is not the fan d&b##6
 2. the person traveling to berlin is not the fan d&b##6
 3. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5
 4. the fan house is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
 6. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the fan classical##3
 9. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the fan d&b##5
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
11. the fan hip-hop is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
12. the fan classical is on the far right##1
13. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
14. the fan house is the person traveling to prague##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the fan house##1
16. the fan pop is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
17. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the fan house##1
18. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
19. the fan d&b is on the right of the fan trance##1
20. the fan soul is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
21. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |    5     |   6    |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | soul     | house     | trance | d&b      | pop    | classical |
| Nationality   | edinburgh | berlin | prague | marseilles | miami | hannover | new-york      |

