.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, water, lemonade, almond-milk, juice, fanta
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, boat, motorbike, skateboard, snowmobile, subway, taxi
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person driving the airplane is not the person drinking sprite##6
14. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
16. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
18. the person drinking juice is not the person driving the motorbike##6
19. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the skateboard##2
20. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |    4    |   5    |     6     |     7      |
| Food        | almond-milk | juice     | sprite | fanta | cola | lemonade    | water   |
| Transport   | taxi      | airplane | skateboard  | boat    | subway | motorbike | snowmobile |

