 1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
12. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
14. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
16. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
17. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
18. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
